==Description==

<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
通过[[Draft_Tray/zh-cn|底图工具栏]]，您可以快速改变[[Draft_Workbench/zh-cn|底图工作台]]对象的可视属性。
</div>

[[Image:Draft_tray_default.png]]
{{Caption|The Draft Tray}}

==Available tools==

* [[Image:Draft_tray_button_plane.png]] [[Draft_SelectPlane|Working Plane]]: selects the current Draft working plane.

* [[Image:Draft_tray_button_style.png]] [[Draft_SetStyle|Set Style]]: sets the default style for new objects.

* [[Image:Draft_tray_button_construction.png]] [[Draft_ToggleConstructionMode|Toggle Construction Mode]]: switches Draft construction mode on or off.

* [[Image:Draft_tray_button_layer.png]] [[Draft_AutoGroup|AutoGroup]]: changes the active [[Draft_Layer|Draft Layer]] or, optionally, the active [[Std_Group|Std Group]] or group-like [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]] object.


